p: Linalyl acetate was found only in V15 and V10, and myrtenyl acetate was found in some accessions in very low concentrations, except in V15. Dihydroeugenyl butanoate was present in V17 and V2. On the other hand, linalyl acetate was present only in two selections, RUM15 and RUM20, and dihydroeugenyl butanoate reached the maximum in RUM12.
